prodNameC: 馬丁彼得游離四碘甲狀腺素試驗系統
ingredientsDesc:
1.	T4 Antibody Coated Tubes, plastic tubes coated with T4 antiserum (rabbit).
2.	Free T4 Serum Standards A-F, containing L-Thyroxine in human serum with 0.1% sodium azide and other preservatives. 
3.	Free T4 Tracer Solution, contains less than 10 μCi per bottle of L-Thyroxine 125I derivative in Tris buffered saline with bovine albumin, EDTA and 0.5% sodium azide and other preservative.
